[SN]TITLE[SN]
Murder arrest after woman dies on A38 in Burton-upon-Trent

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been arrested on suspicion of murder after the death of a woman on a dual carriageway in Staffordshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police said the man, 39, from Hull, had been with her in a van that was pulling into a layby on the A38, near Burton-upon-Trent, on Thursday evening.
As the van was driven in, the woman left the vehicle and was hit by a car.
An air ambulance flew the woman, who has not yet been identified, to hospital with a number of serious injuries. She was later confirmed dead.
